results.title: A resolution designating the week of April 15, 2017, through April 23, 2017, as "National Park Week".
results.short_title: A resolution designating the week of April 15, 2017, through April 23, 2017, as "National Park Week".
results.latest_major_action: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment and with a preamble by Unanimous Consent. (consideration: CR S2352-2353; text: CR S2370)
results.summary: (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Designates April 15-April 23, 2017, as National Park Week. Encourages the people of the United States and the world to visit U.S. national parks.
results.summary_short: (This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary of that version is repeated here.) Designates April 15-April 23, 2017, as National Park Week. Encourages the people of the United States and the world to visit U.S. national parks.
